MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2018-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 9th March, 2018
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 9th March, 2018:
Shri Ashok Gajapathi Raju Pusapati relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister
of Civil Aviation%3B
i)
ii)
The Prime Minister assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Civil Aviation; and
Shri Y. S. Chowdary relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in the
Ministry of Science and Technology; and the office of the Minister of State in the Ministry
iii)
of Earth Sciences.
(Bhaskar Dasgupta)
